<p class="pUA1"><b>Important:</b><br>
The <b>Workflow Items</b> displayed in the <b>Submitted Items</b> folder are items created and 
submitted by you and linked to your <b>UACF ID</b>.  To view <b>all</b> items linked to a specific <b>Consultant Code</b>, click the <b>were submitted for consultant code</b> 
option at the top of the folder, and click the <b>Get list</b> button.</p>

<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=4%><b>Notes</b>:</td>
