<p class="pUA1">You can reopen a closed item in the <b>Closed Items</b> folder by adding a comment to it and resubmitting it, if 
 required.</p>

<p class="pUA1">Follow the procedure below to add a comment to a <b>Closed</b> 
 item:</p>

<table width=100%>

<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=4%>1.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=96%>Ensure that the <b>Closed Items</b> folder is displayed.
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint>2.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>Click the required item to select it.
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
<td>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=4%><b>Tip</b>:</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint width=96%>&nbsp;
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=tdUABullet></td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>You can search for an item by entering the relevant <strong>contract 
 number</strong> or <strong>Workflow number</strong> in the <strong>Only 
 show matches for contract number:</strong> or <strong>workflow number</strong> 
 fields above the folder respectively and click the <strong>Find Now</strong> 
 button
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=tdUABullet></td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>You can scroll through the submitted items list to find the relevant item
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint>3.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>Click the <strong>Add comment</strong> icon on the <b>Closed Items</b> toolbar.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint>&nbsp;</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>A <strong>Comments</strong> area will appear.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint>4.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>Click in the <strong>Comments</strong> area and enter your new comment.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint>5.</td>
<td class=tdUAPoint>Click the <strong>Submit</strong> icon on the <b>Closed Items</b> toolbar.
</td>
</tr>
	
<tr>
<td class=tdUAPoint colspan=2>The comment will be uploaded and the reopened item will be moved back into 
 the <b>Submitted</b> <b>Items</b> folder.</td>
</tr>


</table>

